description: "Two drawings and text from ‘Rerum et urbis Amstelodamensium historia’ by Johannes Pontanus: the port and town of Gamme Lamme on the island of Ternate, with local and European vessels; and a naval battle between Dutch and Portuguese ships."
title: "[View of the island of Ternate with the town Gamme Lamme] / Beniamin W. caelator."
